7-08-18T04:39:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我識有位巴打有用呢隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n陣間幫你召喚佢<br />\n<br />\nXT(手指公波)同DT(食指波)系列粒波都係34mm 巿面上好多手指公波都係34mm<br />\n食指波用34mm有啲細 同埋呢隻DT個控球面積有啲細 不過dpi夠高 你接受到用到就ok<br />\n<br />\n如果你對Elecom啲波有興趣<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">當然其他牌子可能有更好</span><br />\n睇埋隻HT1 新出嘅 大波好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 右鍵比隻DT大啲好㩒啲 不過當然貴啲</blockquote><br />\n初初用會唔會好難上手<br />\n我想買個黎<span style=\"color: red;\">玩下</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過你有決心玩嘅 一個星期已經可以做到文書/網頁瀏覽嗰啲基本冇問題<br />\n如果打機嘅話... 加油努力啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">用緊Elecom HT1URBK / Kensington Expert Mouse打機</span></blockquote><br />\n玩下既話可以留意下logi隻木星  夠平  左右手都用得<br />\n但係手形就無elecom咁好</blockquote><br />\n唔差在睇埋Kensington Orbit <span style=\"color: pink;\">with Scroll Ring</span><br />\n木星有左鍵右鍵+兩粒可自訂鍵+no scroll wheel<br />\nOrbit with Scroll Ring就得左鍵右鍵+Scroll Ring<br />\nScroll Ring幾好用 由其碌fb同睇word文件一流"},{"pid":"c6b6850689674563535854869244f74d6008768a","tid":363947,"uid":23890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T04:40:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">難得有人想揸波</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢隻做入門係唔錯既選擇<br />\n本身好岩手形揸  粒波又唔算拙<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">(都唔算好順)</span><br />\n下一頁/上一頁/scoller左右都唔需要裝野就用得<br />\n係fn掣要裝野再set<br />\n<br />\n如果手指公短既<span style=\"color: red;\">左掣可能會難少少用</span><br />\n其他掣幾好&quot;手禁&quot;<br />\n<br />\n整體手工用料設計對得住價錢<br />\n要注意就係買有線唔好買無線<br />\n無線閒置後tracking會有問題</blockquote><br />\n外國論壇見過有人拆開隻DT黎磨㩒微動開關嗰支actuator 聽講磨完之後左制容易啲㩒<