cken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">唔記得係咪reddit</span></blockquote><br />\n懶鬼廢事攪<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要攪都攪第二隻先</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搞邊隻呀</blockquote><br />\n兩隻Expert<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過要破處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都係拖下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你又知佢處嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a9591a06d3d5200418d1ac0148ab890567ca07f","tid":363947,"uid":100993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T04:57:48.000Z","msg":"指公波感覺上好易攰..<br />\n十幾年前有用過中指波, 記得好似用兩年左右打柴 (其實係花晒碌得唔順)<br />\n<br />\nKensington 好大又好貴, 我要拎出街. deft size 叫接受到... 都係買elecom 呢個試下先.<br />\nbtw, 冇bluetooth 版好撚麻煩, 用notebook 咁就冇左一個usb <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be0a09c9fad28fa41da6632fcad2094e951133c1","tid":363947,"uid":23890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T05:08:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>指公波感覺上好易攰..<br />\n十幾年前有用過中指波, 記得好似用兩年左右打柴 (其實係花晒碌得唔順)<br />\n<br />\nKensington 好大又好貴, 我要拎出街. deft size 叫接受到... 都係買elecom 呢個試下先.<br />\nbtw, 冇bluetooth 版好撚麻煩, 用notebook 咁就冇左一個usb <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nbluetooth你諗都唔洗諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好耐以前出過一隻叫The Ball<br />\n停咗產 基本上揾唔到 同埋聽講造功一般<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n日本依家有隻Digio2 好細隻 用靜音微動<br />\n不過手指公波黎 都唔啱你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n數食指波嘅就得Kensington Expert Mouse Wireless 掉轉隻野粒波會飛出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 完全唔方便攜帶外出<br />\n<br />\n數到嘅都數曬 望就望Logitech會再出多隻trackball 希望有bluetooth<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d68848676f460bb3942ce25f4c441f06e81a032c","tid":363947,"uid":100993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T05:18:02.000Z","msg":"第二日開心使用中.<br />\n用落隻手感覺上冇咁痛.<br />\n<br />\n基本使用, 2個鐘左右就熟習. 係間唔中double click 會陏到個波變左select 幾個file/folder, 跟手幾個file/folder 唔知搬左去邊度... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但用落應該冇呢個問題嘅... 係要啲時間.<br />\n<br />\n個波感覺差少少, 希望唔好咁快花. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3377b02e78a78e0adc421000141b9a726c4fcbb","tid":363947,"uid":23890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T05:44:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第二日開心使用中.<br />\n用落隻手感覺上冇咁痛.<br />\n<br />\n基本使用, 2個鐘左右就熟習. 係間唔中double click 會陏到個波變左select 幾個file/folder, 跟手幾個file/folder 唔知搬左去邊度... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但用落應該冇呢個問題嘅... 係要啲時間.<br />\n<br />\n個波感覺差少少, 希望唔好咁快花. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n恭喜巴打 兩個鐘就習慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n波應該唔易花 除非你掟佢或者揾野刮佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係要定時清老鼠屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}